		'Livros5': 'The Divergent Trilogy is a series of books for young people, involving romance, science fiction and adventure written by Veronica Roth. The story is set in a post-apocalyptic dystopian Chicago. The trilogy is composed of Divergent (2011), Insurgente (2012) and Convergent (2013). ',
		'Livros5p2': 'In the trilogy, society defines its citizens by its social affiliation and personality - featuring five different factions - that eliminate any citizen who can exercise his or her free will or in any way threaten the safety of the population. Beatrice Prior, who later changed her name to Tris, is a young girl born in Abnegation who is transferred to Audacity and must discover the mystery behind the divergent ones, while hiding this true nature, living constantly in danger of being killed if Is discovered by the authorities. ',
