		'Nazismo': 'A Nazi ship that left Brazil was found in Iceland with a certain treasure',
		'TNazismo1': "Nearly eighty years were required for the SS Miden, a sunken German ship to be discovered, some 190 km away from the coast of Iceland. That's because a British company, specializing in locating shipwrecks, Advanced Marine Services was working on site.",
		'TNazismo2': "The discovery has its historical importance, of course. But what's even causing all the frisson around the ship is that it's supposed to be loaded with about 4 tons of gold. That means about 110 million euros (407 million reals). ",
